Getting lost in Rivervale<br>
<br>
Seeing the wooden bridge in NK and thinking, &quot;Thats so cool looking&quot;.<br>
<br>
Getting a big group together to do cube quest in Quynos Sewers for the uber +3 STR Earring (and getting lost down there).<br>
<br>
Human Monks were all there was.<br>
<br>
There were many Trolls, because regen was worth the uglyness.<br>
<br>
100pp for a port to Toxx was a bargin.<br>
<br>
Dying in too far in befallen meant the chance to reroll, because you just lost any hope of getting your corpse back.<br>
<br>
Could make a mule to kill fish in Quynos, then loot fish off corpse to avoid faction hit for Stein quest.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
