<br>
Trying to decide what class to pick..but it was tough since spells weren't documented very well since no one was high enough to have them all yet.<br>
<br>
Hearing the Ice Comet rumors and starting a Wiz.<br>
<br>
Looking for my guild master in neriak for 3 hours...<br>
<br>
Wondering how on earth you could ever lose your corpse. (Stated by my friend that talked me into playing as the worst thing about the game)....then finding out.<br>
<br>
Deciding that nektulos was too crowded, starting a nome, looking for guildmaster in Ak`Anon for 3 hours...<br>
<br>
Damn you broken staff of the observer quest! DAMN YOU!<br>
<br>
Getting discouraged when wizards started hitting 50 and still no ice comet in game....<br>
<br>
Rolling up a necro and having a great time until the dagger nerf <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Crazy crazy necro afk xp....<br>
<br>
Rangers in Lfay.....15pp worth of junk every time, 10 pops, 6 min respawn.....dorfs were even better, but much harder.<br>
<br>
Go tell Roror, &quot;I know no fear!&quot;<br>
<br>
Kalaran hit 50 first, and then changed to Kartak since rogues were the suck, only to get the account banned somewhat after for transfering no drop planar items....then getting furor to 50 in 3ish days (making him a human to prove that there was no advantage to being any certain race).<br>
<br>
Seeing Kalaran's screenshots hanging out next to naggy since you could get naggy faction in SolA (which was changed the next patch).<br>
<br>
FoH killing Vox only to be accused of cheating since Aradune actually fought with them, then being unable to kill Naggy because GM's kept him depopped so one server wouldn't get both first time dragon kills.<br>
<br>
The famous Mithril Circle &quot;stuked&quot; page.<br>
<br>
Being the first person I'd every heard of to hydra (play more than one toon at once), and having people in guk groups not believe me when I told them, &quot;careful of overpulls, I'm the cleric too.&quot;<br>
<br>
They finally put Ice Comet in...and GDI! you have to kill BOTH dragons for the runes...wizards everywhere cried.<br>
<br>
WOOHOO, leet crafted armor for my warrior!<br>
<br>
OMG, the pain of camping all of the cleric quest armor.<br>
<br>
Never having to worry about overpulls since there were 120 people in guk.<br>
<br>
The terror of the Aegis of Life camp...<br>
<br>
Being SO happy to transfer off of Veeshan since it was so disgustingly overcrowded there.<br>
<br>
Krimson's Good v. Evil war...<br>
<br>
Krimson finally proving that the race/hybrid xp penaly was utterly insane taking almost twice as much xp to get to 60 as a non-penalized class.<br>
<br>
Having my manastone poof while pl'ing a wiz <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
