A few rogues picking the HS orb and losing their corpse inside since the key quest wasn't in the game yet.<br>
<br>
When keys weren't soulbound...making going into any zone requiring keys an ordeal.....ESPECIALLY if the key was lore.<br>
<br>
Furor offering to bribe other guilds into trying to kill the Queen in Dok, since they were stuck in VP.<br>
<br>
Epics.....the horror.....the horror.....<br>
<br>
Donal's BP nerf (because the devs are too stupid to realize that if you can cast CH's indefinately every 20 seconds, then you can eventually duo any mob that can't kill your tank in 20 seconds.......i mean, comeon, its not fucking rocket science)<br>
<br>
the next donal's BP nerf (since making it 10 secs longer would surely fix the problem....)<br>
<br>
the next donal's BP nerf....<br>
